## macOS Philosophy

This is the **expanded** version. Everything the iOS app has, plus desktop-exclusive capabilities that leverage the full power of a laptop/desktop:

- **Larger screen** (14-38" ultrawide) → show more, scroll less
- **Keyboard + mouse/trackpad** → precision input, shortcuts for everything
- **Multi-window** → side-by-side workflows, independent state per window
- **Background operation** → persistent processes, menu bar presence
- **Higher compute/memory** → handle heavier features the phone can't

**Design rule:** If you can show it without cluttering, show it. macOS users have the screen space and input precision to handle density.

